used. [CP1]

You can learn the skill "Spark" which deals lightning damage to all enemies when
used. [CP2]

You can learn the technique of "Lightning Slash" which allows you to strike at
an incredible speed that is almost invisible to the eye. [CP1]

You can learn the skill "Cure Poison" which can be used to treat poisoned
allies. [CP1]

You can learn the skill [Regeneration], which promotes cell activation and
enhances regenerative power, by using it. [CP1]

and critical hit rate when used. [CP1]

You can learn the skill "Sleep Mist" which creates a mist that induces
drowsiness in the opponent when used. [CP2]

You can learn the skill "Reflect Armor" which grants allies a suit of armor that
reflects the opponent's offensive magic attacks. [CP2]

equipped weapon when used. [CP2]

weapon when used. [CP2]

You can learn the skill "Enchant Parble" which adds the thunder attribute to the
equipped weapon when used. [CP2]

You can learn the miraculous sword technique [Sacred Sword], which deals damage
to the opponent while healing your own wounds. [CP3]

You can learn the skill "Oil Shock" which spreads oil over a wide area and
covers the opponent in oil. [CP1]

You can learn the skill "Fire Breath" which turns the surroundings into a sea of
fire when used. [CP3]

You can learn the skill "Bizarre Dance" that confuses the opponent when used.
[CP2]

opponent with mysteriously glowing eyes and confuses them. [CP2]

and rotate while kicking the opponent's legs at ground level. [CP2]

confusion, charm, paralysis, and sleep status. [CP1]

all enemies. [CP2]

you to take appropriate stances according to the battle situation. [CP2]
